quran[67]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Ngifunga ngaleli dolobha (Makkah)
  90,2,Futhi wena (uMphrofethi) uvunyelwe kulelidolobha
  90,3,Futhi ngifunga ngomzali kanye nalokho akuzalayo
  90,4,Ngempela samdala umuntu ebunzimeni
  90,5,Ngakube ucabanga ukuthi akasoze abekhona ongaphezulu kwakhe ongamehlula
  90,6,"Uthi, “ngichithe umnotho omningi”"
  90,7,Ngakube ucabanga ukuthi akekho noyedwa ombonayo
  90,8,Asizange yini simenzele amehlo amabili
  90,9,Nolimi nezindebe ezimbili
  90,10,Futhi samholela ezindleleni ezimbili
  90,11,Kepha akakozami ukuhamba endleleni enyukayo (enzima)
  90,12,Futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi indlela eyenyukayo (inzima)
  90,13,Ukukhulula isigqila
  90,14,Noma ukondla ngosuku lwendlala
  90,15,Intandane eyisihlobo
  90,16,Noma umuntu ompofu osothulini (ngenxa yokuhlupheka)
  90,17,Wayeseba ngomunye walabo abakholwayo futhi abayalana ngokubekezela futhi beyalana ngobubele
  90,18,Labo-ke (bangabantu) abangakwesokunene
  90,19,Futhi labo abangakholwanga emavesini (ezimpawini) zethu bona (bangabantu) abangakwesokunxele
  90,20,Phezulu kwabo kunomlilo ovale nhlangothi zonke
  91,1,Ngifunga ngelanga nokucwazimula kwalo
  91,2,Futhi ngifunga ngenyanga uma ililandela (ilanga)
  91,3,Futhi ngifunga ngemini uma ivela
  91,4,Futhi ngifunga ngobusuku uma buyimboza
  91,5,Futhi ngifunga ngesibhakabhaka kanye nalowo owasakha
  91,6,Futhi ngifunga ngomhlaba kanye nalowo owawendlala
  91,7,"Futhi\tngifunga\tngomphefumulo\tkanye\tnalowo owawulinganisa"
  91,8,Wasewukhombisa okubi kwawo kanye nokuhle kwawo
  91,9,Ngempela uphumelele lowo owuhlanzile (umphefumulo wakhe)
  91,10,Futhi ngempela wehlulekile lowo owenze okubi kuwona
  91,11,"(Abantu)\tbaThamud\tbaphika\t(umphrofethi\twabo) ngokungahloniphi"
  91,12,Ngenkathi lowo oyisoni kubona eya phambili
  91,13,"Manjalo sabe sesithi isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi kubona, “Ningalithinti, yikameli lensikazi likaMvelinqangi nesiphuzo salo”"
  91,14,"Ngakho-ke basiphika (isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi) balibulala, manjalo iNkosi yabo yehlisela phezulu kwabo imbubhiso ngenxa yesono sabo yasilinganisa (kubona bonke)"
  91,15,Futhi ayiwesabi umphumela walokho
  92,1,Ngifunga ngobusuku uma bumboza (ngobumnyama)
  92,2,Futhi ngifunga ngemini uma ivela
  92,3,Futhi ngifunga ngalowo owadala isilisa nesifazane
  92,4,Ngempela ukuzabalaza kwenu kwehlukahlukene
  92,5,Mayelana nalowo onikezayo futhi asabe (uMvelinqangi)
  92,6,Futhi akholelwe kokuhle kakhulu
  92,7,Manjalo siyomenzela lula indlela elula
  92,8,Futhi mayelana nalowo oncishanayo futhi ozibona ukuthi
  92,9,Futhi uphika okuhle kakhulu
  92,10,Manjalo siyomenzela lula indlela eya ebunzimeni
  92,11,Futhi ayimsizi ingcebo yakhe uma esewa (efa)
  92,12,Ngempela kuphezulu kwethu ukuholwa
  92,13,Futhi ngempela ngeyethu impilo ezayo neyamanje
  92,14,Ngakho-ke nganexwayisa ngomlilo ovuthayo
  92,15,Akekho oyongena kuwona ngaphandle koyisoni kakhulu
  92,16,Lowo owaphika futhi wafulathela (endleleni eqondile)
  92,17,Futhi uyokuqhelelaniswa nabalungileyo
  92,18,Lowo onikela ngengcebo yakhe ukuze azihlanze
  92,19,Futhi akukho ngisho nakoyedwa kuyena emseni ukuze anikezwe wona
  92,20,"Ngaphandle kokufuna ubuso beNkosi yakhe, ephakeme kakhulu"
  92,21,Futhi uzothokoza
  93,1,Ngifunga ngokukhanya kokusa
  93,2,Futhi ngifunga ngobusuku uma bubamnyama
  93,3,Ayikulahlile iNkosi yakho futhi ayikuzondi
  93,4,Futhi ngempela impilo ezayo ingcono kuwena kuneyamanje
  93,5,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho izokunika ukuze uthokoze
  93,6,Ayikutholanga yini uyintandane yabe seyiyakukhoselisa
  93,7,Futhi yakuthola ulahlekile yabe seyiyakuhola
  93,8,Futhi yakuthola untula umpofu yabe seyiyakunothisa
  93,9,Ngakho-ke intandane ungayicindezeli
  93,10,Futhi mayelana nofuna usizo ungaqhelelani (naye)
  93,11,Futhi ngobubele beNkosi yakho yazisa (abanye)